          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。但不知他此番是好意是歹意？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周德威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里有什么好意，分明是杀人的战场。主公以不去为是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生说哪里话来。倘若孤王不去，岂不被旁人耻笑？孤欲命太保史敬思随同保"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "驾，料无妨碍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，传史敬思进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "史将军进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史敬思",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（史敬思上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史敬思",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "豪杰生来威风凛，上阵能敌百万兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史敬思",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见父王！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾儿少礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史敬思",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周德威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军少礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赐坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史敬思",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢座。宣儿臣上殿，有何国事议论？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今有梁王朱温下书前来，请为父去饮宴。欲命吾儿保驾前往，不知吾儿意下如"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "史敬思",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿臣愿往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周德威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军，那朱温诡计多端，必有埋伏，恐怕将军此去，凶多吉少。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史敬思",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生此言差矣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史敬思",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "先生说的哪里话，"
        },
        {
          "character": "史敬思",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "长他人的威风灭却咱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史敬思",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我把那朱温当作了小娃！"
        },
        {
          "character": "史敬思",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "虎头银枪在某的掌中拿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史敬思",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "要学个单刀赴会走天涯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史敬思",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "大战场见过千千万"
        },
        {
          "character": "史敬思",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "上阵全凭跨下马"
        },
        {
          "character": "史敬思",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "明知此去有奸诈"
        },
        {
          "character": "周德威",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "将军休得夸大话，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周德威",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "朱温武艺果不差。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周德威",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "千万莫要小量他！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周德威",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "大战场见过千千万"
        },
        {
          "character": "周德威",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "上阵全凭跨下马"
        },
        {
          "character": "周德威",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "明知此去有奸诈"
        },
        {
          "character": "周德威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军执意要去，但是一件。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周德威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此去见桥休下马"
        },
        {
          "character": "史敬思",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪一件？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周德威",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此去见桥，且莫下马。务要牢牢谨记。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史敬思",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "记下了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休得多言。带马！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "人来带马前迎道，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "虎穴龙潭走一遭！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李克用、史敬思同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周德威",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "袖内阴阳算得好，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周德威",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "此去只怕他命难逃。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周德威下。）"
        }
      ],
