          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖内喊声〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里有人马呐喊？登高一望！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李克用上，下。四下手、朱温同追上，同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前面败的乃是我父王。后面赶的乃是朱温人马。此时不救，等待何时！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！朱温休得猖狂，你少爷来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李存孝、四龙套同下。）"
